 type_video="local" animate="none" delay="0"][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_empty_space height="30"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_empty_space height="30"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"]<img class="alignleft wp-image-4066 size-full" src="http://dummyimage.com/1920x1080/3498db/3498db.jpg" alt="" width="64" height="64" />[/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text="SOCIAL MEDIA INTEGRATION" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:26|text_align:left|color:%23000000|line_height:1.0" google_fonts="font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1416501508477{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 40px !important;}" el_class="social-media-integration"][vc_empty_space height="10"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"]This theme is big opportunity for your social media debut. Starting from social icons in widgets, buttons and instagram stream in shortcodes to share buttons in blog.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_empty_space height="30"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"]<img class="alignleft wp-image-4067 size-full" src="http://dummyimage.com/1920x1080/f1c40f/f1c40f.jpg" alt="" width="64" height="64" />[/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text="ONE CLICK" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:26|text_align:left|color:%23000000|line_height:1.0" google_fonts="font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1416502054752{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 40px !important;}" el_class="oneclick-import-demo-content"][vc_empty_space height="10"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"]This product include one click option, which allows you to install whole predefined content in just one click, additionally you can choose a different color and mix it.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="full_width" columns_type="wtrMargin" columns_autohight="wtrNoAutoHeightColumns" menu_above="wtrNoAboveMenuRow" bg_type="color" color_bg="#ffffff" img_attr="default" color_overlay_opt="off" color_overlay="rgba(31,206,109,0.6)" parallax="none" type_video="local" animate="none" delay="0"][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_empty_space height="30"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_empty_space height="30"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"]<img class="alignleft wp-image-4062 size-full" src="http://dummyimage.com/1920x1080/2980b9/2980b9.jpg" alt="" width="64" height="64" />[/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text="CUSTOMIZER" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:26|text_align:left|color:%23000000|line_height:1.0" google_fonts="font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1416502196026{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 40px !important;}" el_class="customizer"][vc_empty_space height="10"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"]Change every single colour on page with few clicks. Symetrio uses Customizer that is part of yours WordPress. Modify page with live-view mode. Each change is visible right away.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_empty_space height="30"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"]<img class="alignleft wp-image-4065 size-full" src="http://dummyimage.com/1920x1080/f39c12/f39c12.jpg" alt="" width="64" height="64" />[/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text="MULTI GYM LOCATION" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:26|text_align:left|color:%23000000|line_height:1.0" google_fonts="font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1416502555324{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 40px !important;}" el_class="multi-gym-location"][vc_empty_space height="10"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"]Symetrio supports presenting informactions based on gym location. You can create advanced filters that will connect Trainers / Classes / Class Rooms / Events with one exact location or group. With this function you can create schedules for specified location. Present personel from specified location.\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="full_width" columns_type="wtrMargin" columns_autohight="wtrNoAutoHeightColumns" menu_above="wtrNoAboveMenuRow" bg_type="color" color_bg="#ffffff" img_attr="default" color_overlay_opt="off" color_overlay="rgba(31,206,109,0.6)" parallax="none" type_video="local" animate="none" delay="0"][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_empty_space height="30"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_empty_space height="30"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"]<img class="alignleft wp-image-4064 size-full" src="http://dummyimage.com/1920x1080/2ecc71/2ecc71.jpg" alt="" width="64" height="64" />[/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text="EVENT PAGE" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:26|text_align:left|color:%23000000|line_height:1.0" google_fonts="font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1416502808635{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 40px !important;}" el_class="event-page"][vc_empty_space height="10"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"]You can define organizators and event locations, by that you won`t need to define many times same groups for upcoming events.  We are ahead of your expectations, you don`t need to search for plugins that will allow you to do that. Exclusively for Symetrio we designed module that fits perfectly website.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_empty_space height="30"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"]<img class="alignleft wp-image-4063 size-full" src="http://dummyimage.com/1920x1080/2ecc71/2ecc71.jpg" alt="" width="64" height="64" />[/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text="MENU BELOW" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:26|text_align:left|color:%23000000|line_height:1.0" google_fonts="font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1416502992907{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 40px !important;}" el_class="menu-below"][vc_empty_space height="10"][vc_column_text animate="none" delay="0"]Your header can be unique, and all of this with showing content above the menu bar. Just pick whatever you want and place it on top. Dosen`t matter if you want to use HTML code or Symetrio shortcodes, both will work perfectly. How the header will look like is on you and your creativity.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_empty_space height="120px"][vc_wtr_button label="Purchase Symetrio" align="center" size="big" color="c_green" corner="wtrButtonRad" background="wtrButtonNoTrans" animate_icon="wtrButtonHoverAnim" full_width="wtrButtonNoFullWidth" margin_left="0" margin_right="0" margin_top="0" margin_bottom="0" animate="none" delay="0"][vc_empty_space height="100px"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Features', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3924-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-11 01:15:49', '2015-02-11 01:15:49', '', 3924, 'http://teamlinkmuaythai.dev/3924-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
